article.headline: Alcorn State 72, Texas Southern 67
article.story: ALCORN, Miss. (AP) -- Delvin Thompson scored 24 points to lead Alcorn State to a 72-67 victory over Texas Southern on Wednesday night. Juan Wyatt and Alleo Frazier each added 11 points for Alcorn (2-8, 0-2 SWAC), which overcame a two-point halftime deficit. Sean Walker led Texas Southern (2-10, 1-1) with 22 points, and Mike Sneed added 18.
